<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="E" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Eater" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Eater,</orth> 1) one who eats: <cit><quote>a great e. of beef,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 1.3.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. I, 3, 90</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>of broken meats,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 2, 15</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.130" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 130</bibl>; cf. <emph>to eat</emph> in <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.209" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 209</bibl>.<lb />2) devourer, destroyer: <cit><quote>e. of youth,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 927" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 927</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>